Section: utils
Description: Easily adjust your display brightness and color temperature
 Brightness Controller is the only GUI application 
 for GNU/Linux that allows you to control brightness of
 your primary and secondary display from the same place. 
 It is a software based dimmer. 
 Let your friends know if this application made your 
 display more friendly to your eyes.
